          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Do you ever feel like you’re being pushed around by people while others are taking advantage of niceties and constantly asking you to do things for them? Well ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Say No! More",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is the perfect game to vent those frustrations while also providing a sincere lesson for you to embrace no a bit more in your life. Do you want to stop reading this review and go back to not supporting Switchaboo? NO!!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
