            "text": "Final Score: 82%",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "heading",
        "tag": "h2",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In an industry where crunch is a real issue people often have to deal with and a general work culture of putting the company before yourself, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Say No! More",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " has the relatability to it that genuinely has a good lesson behind it. While the game has a short length and the gameplay is simple, this title is worth playing for a comedic take on serious issues that could be plaguing your own life right now. It’s definitely a title to grab when it comes to a lower price point as it consists of a quick couple hours of humour-filled gameplay and a new perspective to really consider. It’s a shame we don’t review games on a ten point scale, because I would have given ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Say No! More ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "nein",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " out of 10!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
